From Kenneth Sloan Subject Re More gray levels out of the screen In article Jon Rowlands writes A few years ago a friend and I took some grey level photos from a bit Mac Plus screen using this Displaying all levels synchronized to the display took about Why didn't you create grey level images and display them for time slices This requires the same total exposure time and the same precision in timing but drastically reduces the image preparation time no Kenneth Sloan Computer and Information Sciences University of Alabama at Birmingham Campbell Hall UAB Station FAX Birmingham AL